DECLARE @MainMenu VARCHAR(300) = 'Inventory'
DECLARE @SubMenu VARCHAR(300) = 'Reports'
DECLARE @ScreenName VARCHAR(300) ='Amida Report'
IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM PalmsScreen WHERE MainMenu = @MainMenu AND SubMenu = @SubMenu AND ScreenName = @ScreenName)
BEGIN
    INSERT INTO PalmsScreen
    (PalmsModuleID, MainMenu, SubMenu, ScreenName, IsHavingCreateForm, IsHavingActionForm, IsHavingHHT, CreatedBy, CreatedDate, ModifiedBy, ModifiedDate, IsReportForm, IsNotification )
    VALUES
    (1, @MainMenu, @SubMenu, @ScreenName, 1, 0 ,1, 1, GETDATE(), NULL, NULL, 0, 0)
END
GO

-- Adding UI Element
DECLARE @PalmsUIElementCode VARCHAR(100);
DECLARE @PalmsUIElementName VARCHAR(100);
DECLARE @PalmsUIElementPath VARCHAR(100);
DECLARE @UpperPalmsUIElementID INT;
DECLARE @PalmsFeatureID INT;
DECLARE @PalmsUserID INT;
DECLARE @MaxUIElementID INT;

SET @PalmsUIElementCode = 'AmidaReport';
SET @PalmsUIElementName = 'Amida Report';
SET @PalmsUIElementPath = 'Inventory\Reports\AmidaReport';
SET @UpperPalmsUIElementID = (SELECT PalmsUIElementID FROM PalmsUIElement WHERE PalmsUIElementPath = 'Inventory')
SET @PalmsFeatureID = (SELECT PalmsFeatureID FROM PalmsFeature WHERE PalmsFeatureName LIKE '%Inventory%')
SELECT @PalmsUserID = PalmsUserID FROM PalmsUser WHERE PalmsUserLoginName = 'System';
SELECT @MaxUIElementID = MAX(PalmsUIEleMentID) FROM PalmsUIElement;
IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM PalmsUIElement where PalmsUIElementPath=@PalmsUIElementPath)
BEGIN
    DBCC CHECKIDENT ('PalmsUIElement', RESEED, @MaxUIElementID)
    INSERT INTO PalmsUIElement(PalmsUIElementCode, PalmsUIElementName, PalmsUIElementPath, UpperPalmsUIElementID, PalmsFeatureID, IsScreen, IsNotification, CreatedBy, CreatedDate)
    Values(@PalmsUIElementCode, @PalmsUIElementName, @PalmsUIElementPath, @UpperPalmsUIElementID, @PalmsFeatureID, 1, 0, @PalmsUserID, GETDATE())
END
GO

-- Adding the User Type Mapping
DECLARE @PowerUserTypeID INT
DECLARE @WarehouseUserTypeID INT
DECLARE @ScreenID INT
SELECT @PowerUserTypeID = EnumerationValue FROM Enumeration WHERE EnumerationType='UserType' AND EnumerationName='PowerUser'
SELECT @WarehouseUserTypeID = EnumerationValue FROM Enumeration WHERE EnumerationType='UserType' AND EnumerationName='WarehouseUser'
SELECT @ScreenID = PalmsScreenID FROM PalmsScreen WHERE ScreenName = 'Amida Report'

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM PalmsUserTypePalmsScreenMapping WHERE PalmsUserTypeID=@PowerUserTypeID AND PalmsScreenID=@ScreenID)
BEGIN
    INSERT INTO PalmsUserTypePalmsScreenMapping (PalmsScreenID, PalmsUserTypeID, CreatedBy, CreatedDate, ModifiedBy, ModifiedDate)
        VALUES (@ScreenID, @PowerUserTypeID, 1, GETDATE(), NULL, NULL)
END

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM PalmsUserTypePalmsScreenMapping WHERE PalmsUserTypeID=@WarehouseUserTypeID AND PalmsScreenID=@ScreenID)
BEGIN
    INSERT INTO PalmsUserTypePalmsScreenMapping (PalmsScreenID, PalmsUserTypeID, CreatedBy, CreatedDate, ModifiedBy, ModifiedDate)
        VALUES (@ScreenID, @WarehouseUserTypeID, 1, GETDATE(), NULL, NULL)
END
GO

DECLARE @ScreenID INT
DECLARE @ReportName NVARCHAR(50) = 'AmidaReport'
DECLARE @ReportDispalyName NVARCHAR (100) = 'AmidaReport'
DECLARE @ReportRdl VARBINARY(MAX) = 
SELECT @ScreenID = PalmsScreenID FROM PalmsScreen WHERE MainMenu = 'Inventory' AND SubMenu = 'Reports'  AND ScreenName = 'AmidaReport'
IF NOT EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM ReportScreenMapping WHERE PalmsScreenID = @ScreenID AND ReportName = @ReportName)
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO ReportScreenMapping(ReportName, PalmsScreenID, IsDefault, ControlName, CreatedBy, CreatedDate, ReportDispalyName,IsActive,ReportRDL)
	VALUES(@ReportName, @ScreenID, 1, 'Report', 1, GETDATE(), @ReportDispalyName,1,@ReportRdl)
END
GO
